casebody.head_matter:
In Re Tommy R. McGUIRE, petitioner.
No. 16-9567.
Supreme Court of the United States
Oct. 2, 2017.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for writ of mandamus dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
